  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.10.8">
<l>pārēṟu perumpāran tīrap paṇṭu pāratattut tūtiyaṅki pārttaṉ celvat</l>
<l>tērēṟu cāratiyā yetirntār cēṉai cerukkaḷattut tiṟalaḻiyac ceṟṟāṉ ṟaṉṉai</l>
<l>pōrēṟoṉ ṟuṭaiyāṉu maḷakaik kōṉum purantaraṉum nāṉmukaṉum poruntu mūrppōl</l>
<l>cīrēṟu maṟaiyāḷar niṟainta celvat tirukkōva lūrataṉuḷ kaṇṭēṉ nāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one who, as a charioteer mounted the opulent chariot of Partha,</l>
<l rend="indent">having traveled as a messenger in the Bharata [War] long ago</l>
<l>To end the great burden that appeared on the earth,</l>
<l rend="indent">	destroyed the enemy army, when their strength failed on the battlefield,</l>
<l>I saw in prosperous Tirukkōvalūr, filled with excellent Vedic experts,</l>
<l>Like the city where abides [Śiva] with a battle bull, [Kubera], king of Aḷakai,</l>
<l rend="indent">[Indra], the fort-breaker, and four-faced [Brahmā].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
